  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Butter Muffin</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>A <b>Butter Muffin</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetable\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetable\">Vegetable</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butterfly_Wings\" title=\"Butterfly Wings\">Butterfly Wings</a> and 1 Vegetable. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\n</p><p>Adding any <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meatballs\" title=\"Meatballs\">Meatballs</a> and possibly other recipes while adding a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\">Mandrake</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a>. Adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragon_Fruit\" title=\"Dragon Fruit\">Dragon Fruit</a> may result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragonpie\" title=\"Dragonpie\">Dragonpie</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wings\" title=\"Wings\"><img alt=\"Wings.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wings.png?a189ea\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot(No Mandrake).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot%28No_Mandrake%29.png?2138af\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot.png?bb1767\" width=\"580\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wings\" title=\"Wings\"><img alt=\"Wings.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wings.png?a189ea\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter_Muffin\" title=\"Butter Muffin\"><img alt=\"Butter Muffin.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Butter_Muffin.png?c6184a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Example\">Example</span></h2>\n<tab