  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nButter Muffin\nFood Info\n37.5\n20\n5\nVeggie\nObject Info\n15 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x2\n40 sec\n1\nMiscellaneous\n\"butterflymuffin\"\n“I threw the recipe away and just kind of winged it.”\n–Wilson\n“Heehee, look at that butterfly stuck in the muffin.”\n–Willow\n“Wolfgang did not know about bug muffin. I will taste.”\n–Wolfgang\n“Let's see you get out of this sugary trap!”\n–Wendy\n“THE INNOCENCE ADDS FLAVOR”\n–WX-78\n“Who knew butterflies made such nice baked goods?”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Crunchy! ...But soft?”\n–Woodie\n“That should stop its incessant flapping.”\n–Maxwell\n“A curative confectionary. And one I can eat!”\n–Wagstaff\n“Muffin, smuffin.”\n–Wigfrid\n“Do you know the muffin spider?”\n–Webber\n“What a pretty muffin!”\n–Walani\n“Delectable!”\n–Warly\n“Fibre gives ye wings.”\n–Woodlegs\n“MUFFINS 'TIS CRUNCHY”\n–Wilba\n“Yummm...”\n–Wormwood\n“Swell. It comes with butterfly frosting.”\n–Wheeler\n“Never liked having butterflies in my stomach.”\n–Winona\n“Muffin to see here, my dear.”\n–Wortox\n“Tasty!”\n–Wurt\n“I feel kind of bad about the butterfly.”\n–Walter\n“It has a subtle taste, light and fleeting.”\n–Wanda\nA Butter Muffin is a Vegetable Food item cooked in the Crock Pot by combining 1 Butterfly Wings and 1 Vegetable. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\nAdding any Meats will result in Meatballs and possibly other recipes while adding a Mandrake will result in Mandrake Soup. Adding 1 Dragon Fruit may result in Dragonpie.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×2\nExample[edit | edit source]\n×2\nA recipe for Butter Muffin that extenuates hunger value\n50% chance to result in Stuffed Eggplant\n50% chance to result in Dragonpie\n×2\n×2\nUsage[edit | edit source]\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
