  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|foodType = [[Veggie]] [[File:Veggie.png|32px|]]\n|icon = {{FULLPAGENAME}}.png\n|image = {{FULLPAGENAME}} Dropped.png\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Wings}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Vegetables}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|spoil = 15 Days\n|stack = 40\n|hpRestored = 20\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime = 40 sec\n|priority = 1\n|crafting = Cooked in a [[Crock Pot]]\n|spawnCode = \"butterflymuffin\"\n|canBeBurned=1\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = I threw the recipe away and just kind of winged it.\n|willow = Heehee, look at that butterfly stuck in the muffin.\n|wolfgang = Wolfgang did not know about bug muffin. I will taste.\n|wendy = Let's see you get out of this sugary trap!\n|wx78 = THE INNOCENCE ADDS FLAVOR\n|wickerbottom = Who knew butterflies made such nice baked goods?\n|woodie = Crunchy! ...But soft?\n|maxwell = That should stop its incessant flapping.\n|wagstaff = A curative confectionary. And one I can eat!\n|wigfrid = Muffin, smuffin.\n|webber = Do you know the muffin spider?\n|walani = What a pretty muffin!\n|warly = Delectable!\n|woodlegs = Fibre gives ye wings.\n|wilba = MUFFINS 'TIS CRUNCHY\n|wormwood = Yummm...\n|wheeler = Swell. It comes with butterfly frosting.\n|winona = Never liked having butterflies in my stomach.\n|wortox = Muffin to see here, my dear.\n|wurt = Tasty!\n|walter = I feel kind of bad about the butterfly.\n|wanda = It has a subtle taste, light and fleeting.\n|choose = wx78\n}}\nA '''Butter Muffin''' is a [[Vegetable]] [[Food]] [[item]] cooked in the [[Crock Pot]] by combining 1 [[Butterfly Wings]] and 1 Vegetable. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\n\nAdding any [[Meats]] will result in [[Meatballs]] and possibly other recipes while adding a [[Mandrake]] will result in [[Mandrake Soup]]. Adding 1 [[Dragon Fruit]] may result in [[Dragonpie]]. \n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Wings.png|link=Wings]]\n* Requires: [[File:Vegetables Crock Pot(No Mandrake).png|link=Vegetables]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Meats Crock Pot.png|link=Meat]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Mandrake.png|link=Mandrake]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Wings\n|item2 = Vegetables\n|item3 = Filler\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Butter Muffin\n|count2 = 1\n}}\n== Example ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butterfly Wings\n|item2 = Red Cap\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Butter Muffin\n|note={{Pic24|Prototype}} A recipe for Butter Muffin that extenuates hunger value}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butterfly Wings\n|item2 = Carrots\n|item3 = Berry\n|item4 = Eggplants\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Butter Muffin\n|note = 50% chance to result in [[Stuffed Eggplant]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butterfly Wings\n|item2 = Carrots\n|item3 = Dragon Fruit\n|item4 = Berry\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Butter Muffin\n|note = 50% chance to result in [[Dragonpie]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butterfly Wings\n|item2 = Carrots\n|item3 = Ice\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Butter Muffin\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butterfly Wings SW\n|item2 = Seaweed\n|item3 = twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Butter Muffin\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n|note=}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item = Butter Muffin\n|tool = Pig Icon\n|result = Manure\n}}\n\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nCD butterflymuffin.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\nButter Muffin 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\n</gallery>\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[de:Buttermuffin]]\n[[fr:Muffin au beurre]]\n__NOTOC__\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]"
